_CQ">Hoạ Trị Bình phủ viện Thúc Thuyên thị Ưng Tôn Nhâm Thân cửu nhật nguyên vận - 和治平撫院叔荃氏膺蓀壬申九日原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Lan-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C3%A0i-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-_0kVqenJGRyi535nuJrk6g">Sài Sơn tự - 柴山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Lan-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-nd0Dc2rDm_CVSYltcv5irQ">Lan Hương thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-c%E1%BB%95-ca/poem-SQLcZneUoty6Zn7UCfgM4Q">Thạch cổ ca - 石鼓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ti%E1%BB%81n-cam-c%C3%BAc-hoa/poem-R2L4Kx7Gu8zfMS7CPUAHkA">Thán đình tiền cam cúc hoa - 嘆庭前甘菊花　</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/Ti%E1%BB%81u-t%E1%BA%A9u/poem-AgLChDOmX7lqheFC7GtE4Q">Tiều tẩu - 樵叟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/author-SWshGEoAx645s4epx95yPA">Quán Hưu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
